      <title>政治风险依然存在，投资者纷纷避开法国市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/investors-shun-french-markets-as-political-risk-still-lingers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国资产继续大幅折价，总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁 (Francois Bayrou) 应对持续的政治危机的努力还远远不足以让投资者回归。要想让投资者回归，需要制定切实的计划来削减法国庞大的预算赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/investors-shun-french-markets-as-political-risk-still-lingers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 07:45:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Taylor Wimpey 的 2024 年英国房屋销售接近预期最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/taylor-wimpey-s-uk-home-sales-near-top-end-of-guidance-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰勒温佩公司 (Taylor Wimpey Plc) 表示，其 2024 年房屋销售额将接近此前预期的上限，这为英国房屋建筑商在度过又一个艰难的一年后提供了一些安慰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/taylor-wimpey-s-uk-home-sales-near-top-end-of-guidance-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 07:39:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
