      <title>国际能源署对俄罗斯减产发出警告且库存下降，油价维持涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-16</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对全球供应风险的担忧日益加剧，且美国商业原油库存出现 2021 年以来最长的连续下降，油价年初大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-16</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 23:31:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息预期和企业盈利提振推动股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国核心通胀降温使美联储今年放松政策的前景保持活力，且积极的盈利消息提振了市场人气，全球股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 22:22:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>开云集团将巴黎地标建筑的股份出售给 Ardian</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/kering-sells-majority-stake-in-three-paris-properties-to-ardian</link>
      <description><![CDATA[开云集团 (Kering SA) 同意将巴黎三处豪华地产的多数股权出售给法国私募股权公司 Ardian SAS，这笔交易将为陷入困境的古驰 (Gucci) 时尚品牌所有者带来 8.37 亿欧元（8.61 亿美元）的净收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/kering-sells-majority-stake-in-three-paris-properties-to-ardian</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 17:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管特朗普征收关税，中国富裕省份仍着眼于 2025 年实现强劲增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/china-s-regions-set-bullish-2025-growth-goal-in-guide-for-nation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国五个最重要的省份表示，计划今年的经济增长率达到或超过5%，这表明尽管贸易逆风日益加剧，中国仍将制定雄心勃勃的国家目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/china-s-regions-set-bullish-2025-growth-goal-in-guide-for-nation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 06:32:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
